thread.title: Cecelia

author: Cecelia
title: Cecelia
text: I found Willis Orchand by searching online for a specific tree I wanted to give to my mother for Christmas. I knew it wasn't safe to plant but some companies would have sent it anyway. Willis Orchards waited until,it was safe to plant in her zone. They notified me promptly of the shipment. It arrived at my mom's house in good condition. She got it planted easily. Very satisfied!
